title: Commercial CHEF CHM770W Counter Top Microwave Oven, 0.7 Cubic Feet, White
description: Just the Right Size, Just the Right Features. This Commercial Chef countertop microwave oven delivers 700 watts of power and the quality. Great for a small kitchen or dorm room, this unit provides the benefit of convenient features you would find on a larger microwave without taking up too much counter space. The keypad controls give you the option of inputting precise cook times, and the LED display lets you clearly see exactly how much time is left. 6 one-touch quick cook buttons for items like popcorn and frozen dinners add to the convenience, and the child safety lock ensures the microwave is not used without supervision.
